#CAMERA 11
#phrase Haburu 5
What the wind has carried away won't come back, and it's not worth talking about. But what can be fixed is far more important.
#CAMERA 11
#phrase Haburu 6
Where people have built many houses, and what you call manufactories, there are many dog cages in the northwest.
#CAMERA 11
#phrase Haburu 7
Power and fear force the poor animals to serve. But it's inappropriate. Just as our dear unicorns come to us of their own accord, so should dogs choose their own hosts.